pageContext.claim: “If you look at Secretary General Stoltenberg's remarks, he was very generous in his remarks about what I've done for NATO and what our country has done, but what I've done in terms of getting other countries to put up money -- because they weren't putting up money, and now they put up money at a level like has never been seen before, actually.”
pageContext.analysis: False. NATO Secretary-General Stoltenberg made no such remark.
